    "description": "羞涩的巨佬Denisyich出发前往一个未知的街道，不仅要击败破坏蛋白质供应的神秘敌人，还要找到真正的朋友。用你巨大的拳头击败敌人，收集效果不明的奇怪物品，并出于好心帮助可疑的角色，因为只有你能拯救你心爱的健身房！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终极的巨佬力量</h2> 强大的肌肉和忠诚的嗜血伙伴——作为健身房的孩子，这就是你完美的初始装备包，难道你还需要更多吗？增强你的体能，成为城市街道上最强大的巨佬。没有枪支和剑——只有你巨大的拳头和意志力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/bf7acd54237b207a1468f7c442bee446.poster.avif?t=1757587271\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/bf7acd54237b207a1468f7c442bee446.webm?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/bf7acd54237b207a1468f7c442bee446.mp4?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不可预测的神器</h2> 探索世界，找到超过?件具有完全不可预测效果的物品。每次发现都可能帮助或伤害你，你必须亲身体验才能知道结果！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/2d57f9febe3750541d1d679a327bf968.poster.avif?t=1757587271\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/2d57f9febe3750541d1d679a327bf968.webm?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/2d57f9febe3750541d1d679a327bf968.mp4?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狂野的故事任务</h2> 投入到令人激动的任务中：遇见健身狂热者，拯救被欺负的小人物，摧毁秘密地下实验室，等等。每一次冒险都是拯救健身房和揭开城市秘密的一步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/7165d2b46f23462d69f30a217d5dd005.poster.avif?t=1757587271\" width=518 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/7165d2b46f23462d69f30a217d5dd005.webm?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/7165d2b46f23462d69f30a217d5dd005.mp4?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未探索的世界</h2> 克服社交焦虑，探索新地点。在城市公园中不要迷路，在流浪汉之王的街区制造麻烦，或只是跑到商店买牛奶！每个新区域都会以其居民和任务让你惊喜，但要小心——不是所有人都愿意成为朋友！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/1fe5779abea046338328e5c238e63d28.poster.avif?t=1757587271\" width=622 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/1fe5779abea046338328e5c238e63d28.webm?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032360/extras/1fe5779abea046338328e5c238e63d28.mp4?t=1757587271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限的乐趣</h2> 这个世界上的梗图、奇怪的物品和荒诞的居民不会让你有一秒钟感到无聊，尤其是他们试图杀死你的时候！在你为蛋白质天堂的幸福而战时，享受幽默和混乱吧！",
